---
// Inline formula chip — `<Formula>log₂ N</Formula>` for small math runs that
// shouldn't break across lines. For block-level math, use a fenced code block
// or a <pre>.
---
<span
  class="rounded-sm bg-rule-soft px-1.5 py-px font-mono text-[0.95em] text-ink whitespace-nowrap max-md:whitespace-normal"
>
  <slot />
</span>
